data.description: This is your chance to own a beautiful, recently updated home in the heart of Winter Springs! Nestled in a peaceful and friendly neighborhood, this charming residence offers a unique blend of comfort, style, and convenience. With 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious interior, this home is perfect for families seeking a cozy and elegant living space. The Living Room is designed for relaxation and social gatherings, offering a comfortable space with high ceilings and plenty of natural light. There is also a Wood-Burning Fireplace to add ambience for get-togethers with family and friends, or a romantic evening for two. The Kitchen is a chef’s delight featuring Granite Countertops, a beautiful Glass Tile Backsplash, Stainless Steel appliances, including a new Refrigerator, new Stove, and new, large Stainless-Steel Sink as well as plenty of Cabinet Space. It's the heart of the home, perfect for creating delicious meals and unforgettable memories. The Master Bedroom is located on one side of the home, offering extra privacy. It includes an oversized Walk-In Closet with plenty of space for clothing and storage. The Master Bathroom was recently renovated and includes a Dual Vanity, and a beautiful, custom Tile Shower with Glass Door.  Three additional Bedrooms can be found on the opposite side of the home, each offering plenty of space and ample closet room for clothes. The Garage has been professionally converted into a very large Bonus room that could serve as a Home Office, additional Bedroom, a Family/Game Room, or a Home Gym! Directly off the Living Room/Kitchen you’ll find a spacious Florida Room with lots of windows for great natural light and its own split-unit AC system allowing you to have complete control over the temperature in the room. The Florida Room overlooks and opens to a private, screened Lanai complete with an in-ground Pool that includes a Pool Heater and new Pool Liner. The large, fenced backyard is a perfect haven for grilling, gardening, or simply unwinding and there are no rear neighbors as the property backs up to a nature area. There is even a Storage Shed in place for keeping outdoor tools and equipment neatly and safely out of sight. Additional Extras include - Wired Security Cameras, and a fully functioning Tesla EV Charger should you own or plan to own an electric vehicle. For added convenience the home has several Smart components in place, including a Google Nest device, Smart Door lock on the front door, and a Smart Thermostat to allow you compete control of the home’s AC & Heating system from anywhere. Other recent upgrades include a New Water Heater in 2020, New Windows in 2021, and a New HVAC system with new Ducts in 2019. This home is ideally located close to top-rated schools, parks, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Commuters will appreciate the easy access to major highways, and there is even a dedicated Parking Space to the left of the house that would be perfect for a Boat, Camper, or RV. All of this, PLUS, NO HOA to contend with! Don't miss this opportunity to make 624 Pearl Rd your forever home. It's a rare find in Winter Springs, offering a blend of modern amenities and a warm, inviting atmosphere. Schedule a showing today and experience the magic of this beautiful property for yourself!
